name: Sullivan Michael Christopher
description: Honestly I don’t know how I’m going to describe my personality here in a few sentences but I will try. I am warm, enthusiastic, very passionate and excited about new ideas and people. I am creative person and I like to bring beauty to everything! I have many skills and talents; I am very bright and intuitive. I want to take pleasure of every minute of my life and I can say for sure that I LOVE TO LIVE
